item.title: Official Hige Dandism - Subtitle (Romaji, Furigana, and Translation)
item.description: Subtitle is a Japanese song by the band Official Hige Dandism, released on their album "Traveler" in 2019. The song is a blend of pop, rock, and jazz genres, featuring upbeat instrumentation and catchy melodies.
